Short: Virtual Ball Fighters RTG Demo Version
Uploader: Stefano Tamascelli xtreme@netbusiness.it
Author: Stefano Tamascelli xtreme@netbusiness.it
Type: game/think
Requires: OS3.x+, 68040+, 8Mb Fast, AHI, RTGMaster 42.0+, GFXBoard 

This is the Virtual Ball Fighters demo version.

WARNING!!!!!!! In this demo you have to use only the keyboard for the input.
ASSIGN VBF: <path where is VBFGame >
ASSIGN FONTS: VBF:FONTS ADD

***********************************************
* REQUIREMENTS ( DEMO VERSION )
***********************************************
AGA Version
---------------------

- An Amiga 68030+ with OS 3.0+, AGA ,4 Mb of FastRam and AHI ( not included ).

- Suggested: 68040, 8MB of FastRam.


RTG Version
---------------------
- An Amiga 68040+ with OS 3.0+, 8 Mb of Fast Ram, RTGMaster v42.0 o more ( not included )
  and AHI ( not included ).

- Suggested: 68040, 8 Mb FastRam.

***********************************************
* REQUIREMENTS ( FULL VERSION )
***********************************************

- CDRom 6x ( Suggested 10x )

- Joystick ( Suggested Joypad )


AGA Version
---------------------

- An Amiga 68030+ with OS 3.0+, AGA ,4 Mb of FastRam and AHI ( not included ).

- Suggested: 68040, 8MB of FastRam.


RTG Version
---------------------
- An Amiga 68040+ with OS 3.0+, 8 Mb of Fast Ram, RTGMaster v42.0 o more ( not included )
  and AHI ( not included ).

- Suggested: 68040, 8 Mb FastRam.


**********************************************
* FULL VERSION FEATURES
**********************************************

- OS System friendly (run in multitasking).

- 8 fighters with 8 backgrounds.

- 6 Game Modes
    ( 1 Vs 1 )
    ( Story )
    ( Battle )
    ( Survival )
    ( Time Dead )
    ( Mortal )

- 4 difficult levels.

- 8 Artificial Intelligence Level.

- 10 Features for every Fighter ( very important for the developement of the game )
    ( Name )
    ( Age )
    ( Job )

    ( Power )
    ( Speed )
    ( Rotation )
    ( Energy )
    ( Intelligence )
    ( Luck )
    ( Special )

- 8 audio tracks ( once for background ) + 5 audio tracks on the game ( over 40 minutes ).

- Code optimized for :
    68030 ( only AGA )
    68040 ( AGA and RTG )
    68060 ( only RTG )
    PPC   ( only RTG )

- Over 45Mb of graphics ( AGA Version ).

- Over 70Mb of graphics ( RTG Version ).

- Over 2Mb of sounds.

- AHI and RTGMaster suppport.

- with GFX cards run on 16bits and 24bits ( 640x480 )

- Very intuitive control method.

- More than 100 frames of animation for every fighter.

- Over 400 Mb of Incredible animations ( 3 versions for movie ).


Install the demo
----------------
Assign VBF:
Assign FONTS: VBF:Fonts add


Controls
----------------

Only keyboard ( only demo version )

Cursor Left     -   Left
Cursot Right    -   Right
Cursor Down     -   Fast Down
SHIFT           -   Rotate the ball
AMIGA           -   Rotate the ball
ALT             -   Rotate the ball

P               -   Pause
ESC             -   Quit game
S               -   Sound on/off

Play the demo
-------------

3 Rounds, human vs computer, Alice vs Alice.

Allign 3 balls of the same color.
Collect the bonus :
A   -   Input malfunction ( the controls are inverted )
B   -   Bonus x 2
D   -   Decrease Speed
E   -   Increase energy
I   -   Increase enemy speed
S   -   Special Blows

